.Sh NAME
.Nm vttest
.Nd "test VT100-type terminal"
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility is a program designed to test the functionality of a
.Tn VT100
terminal
(or emulator thereof).
